unittitle_ssm: Brooklyn Historical Society collection of genealogical records
abstract_ssm: The collection consists of genealogical records relating to Brooklyn families that have been collected by Brooklyn Historical Society, dating from 1892 to 1998. Families include Allen, Bueker, Foster, Greene, Metz, Sparacino, Walker, and others. Types of materials include death certificates, marriage certificates, photographs, and clippings.
